2단,3단 레이아웃 만들기
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>3단 레이아웃</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
       #wrapper {
            width: 1200px;
            /* border: 1px solid gray; */
       }
       #header{
            width: 100%;
            height: 120px;
            background: #ccc;
       }
       #sidebar-left {
            width: 250px;
            height: 600px;
            background: #aaa;
            float: left;
       }
       #sidebar-right {
            width: 150px;
            height: 600px;
            background: #aaa;
            float: right;
       }
       #content {
            width: 800px;
            height: 600px;
            background: #646464;
            float: left;
       }
       #footer {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100px;
            background: #ccc; 
            clear: both;
       }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="wrapper">
        <div id="header">헤더</div>
        <div id="sidebar-left">왼쪽 사이드바</div>
        <div id="sidebar-right">오른쪽 사이드바</div>
        <div id="content">본문</div>
        <div id="footer">푸터</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

position 활영하여 글자 옮기기
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>CSS float 속성</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/position-2.css">
</head>

<body>
  
    <div id="contents" style="position: relative; width: 800px; height: 500px; margin: 0 auto; background: url('images/bg.jpg') no-repeat center/cover;">
      <h1 style="position: absolute; top: 35%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); color: #fff; font-size: 120px; text-shadow: 2px 3px 0 #000;">CSS3</h1>      
    </div>
</body>
</html>

박스테두리를 활용하여 나누기
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>여간 시간 즐기기</title>
  <style>
    a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #222;
    }
    #travel {
      width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .title-text {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .title-text > h2 {
      font-size: 2.5em;
      color: #919191;
    }
    .title-text > p {
      font-size: 0.95em;
      color: #ccc;
      margin-top: 10px;
      
      
    }
    .travel-list {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 20px;
      padding-top: 30px; 
    }    
    .travel-card img {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
      margin: 0 auto ;
      display: block;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }
    .travel-card p {
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .travel-card {
     width: 250px;
     border: 1px solid #ddd; 
     border-radius: 15px;
     padding: 10px;
    text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="travel">
    <div class="title-text">
      <h2>여가 시간 즐기기</h2>
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Non, in! Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="travel-list">
      <div class="travel-card">
        <a href="#">
          <img src="images/tr-1.png">
          <h3>도심 투어</h3>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit. Lorem ipsum dolor sit.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="travel-card">
        <a href="#">
          <img src="images/tr-2.png">
          <h3>바다 즐기기</h3>
          <p> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="travel-card">
        <a href="#">
          <img src="images/tr-3.png">
          <h3>등산 도전하기</h3>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet. Lorem, ipsum dolor.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="travel-card">
        <a href="#">
          <img src="images/tr-4.png">
          <h3>관광지 투어</h3>
          <p>Lorem, ipsum dolor. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.</p>
        </a>
      </div>    
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

현재까지 배운거 종합적으로 외부스타일 적용하기
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>상품 소개 페이지</title>
  <style>
      * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: "Apple SD Gothic Neo", "Malgun Gothic", "맑은 고딕", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      color: #333;
    }

    #container {
      max-width: 820px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .section-box {
      background-color: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #dcdcdc;
      border-radius: 20px 20px 0px 0px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }


    .section-box2 {
      background-color: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #dcdcdc;
      border-radius: 0px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
        .section-box3 {
      background-color: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #dcdcdc;
      border-radius:  0px 0px 20px 20px  ;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .section-box:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .section-inner {
      padding: 30px 50px;
    }

    
    #content .image-wrap img {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }

    h1,
    h2 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    #content h1 {
      font-size: 30px;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    
    #package table {
      width: 700px;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      table-layout: fixed;
    }

    #package caption {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      text-align: left;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #333;
      caption-side: top;
    }

    #package th,
    #package td {
      border: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }

    #package th {
      background-color: #fafafa;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
    }

    #package td {
      text-align: left;
    }

    
    .title-text {
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="container">
    <section id="content" class="section-box">
      <div class="image-wrap">
        <img src="/images/tangerines.jpg" alt="레드향">
      </div>
      <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="content-text">
          <h1>레드향</h1>
          <p>껍질에 붉은 빛이 돌아 <strong>레드향</strong>이라 불린다.</p>
          <p>레드향은 <em>한라봉과 귤을 교배</em>한 것으로<br>일반 귤보다 2~3배 크고, 과육이 붉고 통통하다.</p>
          <p>비타민 C와 비타민 P가 풍부해<br><strong>혈액순환, 감기예방</strong> 등에 좋은 것으로 알려져 있다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="recipe" class="section-box2">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <h2>레드향 샐러드 레시피</h2>
        <p><strong>재료 :</strong> 레드향 1개, 아보카도 1개, 토마토 1개, 샐러드 채소 30g</p>
        <p><strong>드레싱 :</strong> 올리브유 1큰술, 레몬즙 2큰술, 꿀 1큰술, 소금 약간</p>
        <ol>
          <li>샐러드 채소를 씻고 물기를 제거한 후 준비합니다.</li>
          <li>레드향과 아보카도, 토마토를 먹기 좋은 크기로 썰어둡니다.</li>
          <li>드레싱 재료를 믹서에 갈아줍니다.</li>
          <li>볼에 샐러드 채소와 썰어 둔 레드향, 아보카도, 토마토를 넣고 드레싱을 뿌리면 끝!</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="package" class="section-box3">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <h2>상품 구성</h2>
        <table>
          <caption style="text-align: center; margin-left: -80px; margin-bottom: -0.5px">선물용과 가정용 상품 구성</caption>
          <colgroup>
            <col style="background-color:#f5f5f5;">
            <col>
            <col style="width:140px">
            <col style="width:140px">
            <col style="width:150px">            
          </colgroup>
          <thead >
            <tr >
              <th>용도</th>
              <th>중량</th>
              <th>갯수</th>
              <th>가격</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td rowspan="2">선물용</td>
              <td>3kg</td>
              <td>11~16과</td>
              <td>35,000원</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>5kg</td>
              <td>18~26과</td>
              <td>52,000원</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td rowspan="2">가정용</td>
              <td>3kg</td>
              <td>11~16과</td>
              <td>30,000원</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>5kg</td>
              <td>18~26과</td>
              <td>47,000원</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
